title: WinMugen [Features Additional Chars and Stages] 1.5GB
description:
WinMugen "Starter" Kit

My custom WinMugen w/ additional characters and stages added.
Approximately 115 characters and 31 extra stages (including Duck Hunt and Strength Training). Some of the characters included are very rare and no longer publicly available. Most characters are completed, a few are incomplete and slightly buggy.

This is mainly purposed as my own personal dump of my custom WinMugen, so there are custom edits and add-ons included as well.

If you do choose this, please enjoy and seed.
